# Direct dependencies for the Sitara API (runtime + development in one
# understandable list). The installable lock is requirements.txt, generated
# from this file with pinned pip-tools — regenerate on Windows with:
#
#   docker run --rm -v "${PWD}\apps\api:/app" -w /app python:3.12.7-slim-bookworm `
#     sh -c "pip install pip-tools==7.4.1 && pip-compile --generate-hashes --output-file requirements.txt requirements.in"
#
# CI fails if requirements.txt is stale relative to this file.

